<br>
I think that closed bidding, with the points being announced at the end of the raid or at the end of the bid working fine.  It makes it the bidding independedent and people are only going to bid what they believe the subjective value to them will be.  Therefore, although I voted for open bidding, because I like the open information, I prefer closed bidding (i.e. one bid, then announcing openly).  <br>
<br>
