<br>
My first point is that the auctioneer can not bid for items, without compromising his/her integrity. Even bidding ALL your points for an item will allow someone to call foul. <br>
---------------------<br>
For example; in a closed auction system;<br>
<br>
Auctioneer_001 wants Uber_Item, therefore he decides to bid 18 of the 20 total points he has. <br>
<br>
In the ensuing bidding Scarab_002 bids all 19 points she has.<br>
<br>
It can be seen that Auctioneer_001 can easily exploit the situation in a closed auction, with a simple modification of his bid.<br>
